DESCRIPTION:Electro-pop & spoken-word artist Creature & Machine curates an evening of acoustic and spoken word performances from emerging artists around the theme of ___Quiet Power___. Expect haunting vocals, luscious harmonies and intimate poetry from an eclectic line-up of up-and-coming music and spoken word artists.
